        "text": "rapismasin eballon, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Mark 14:65",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". See the prophecy of ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Isaiah 1:6",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The Priests of that day, and their pampered followers, were too much addicted to these brutalities (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Acts 21:32",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Acts 23:2",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), as we learn also from the Talmud.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
